headline: Eric Naaman of Damotech Wins EY 2025 Entrepreneur Of The Year速 Eastern Overall Award
summary: MONTREAL, October 15, 2025--Damotech proudly celebrates CEO Eric Naaman's nomination as EY Entrepreneur Of The Year速 2025 Eastern Overall Award winner. The EY Canada program honours visionary leaders whose purpose-driven innovations transform industries, create jobs, and strengthen communities.
